snippet.title: [ArcheWorld] The Adventure of Moa: 1. Customizing
snippet.description:
Hi everyone!

This is Moa.
Before exploring the ArcheWorld, you may have to create your own character first!
Let’s see what customizing options and classes we have in ArcheWorld.
If you are ready, let’s go!

[Links]
Join ArcheWorld: https://asia.archeworld.com/
ArcheWorld Discord: https://discord.com/invite/gQbHufwehX
